race.description: The Gable Inn Country Boosted Mdn Hcp
race.comment: TERRITORY STYLE (3) just missed at Armidale and then was outgraded at Rosehill. Has a soft gate and the blinkers on for the first time. Presents fitter again and is feared back to country level. BELLERATA (8) resumed over 1000m at Muswellbrook, beaten a long neck. Has the inside barrier and won't have to improve much to be a winning chance. TRUCE (6) debuts and looked good when he won a recent 900m trial at the track. The race-day betting will be key with her and with the other first-timers. MASTER SPEED (1) gelding by Deep Field on debut. Purchased for AUD $ 140,000 (Magic Millions 2023 Gold Coast 2YOs In Training Sale). Recent trial winner at Muswellbrook. Include.
